{"id":233011082,"title":"我媽把我東西毀了","content":"我目前是跟白沙屯媽祖走\n我家人沒有非常同意我怎麼做\n但我也少去宮裡\n大概平均兩個月一次\n有媽祖活動才會去幫忙的那種\n昨天媽祖盛事剛結束\n我帶了求的米回來\n我媽又很生氣\n叫我不要再去了裝神弄鬼\n結果回家\n她把我貼在房間的媽祖海報撕掉了\n然後把我求的米給亂灑\n請問會不會怎麼樣？\n/\n家人問題放一邊\n我的米跟海報這樣被毀了\n會不會發生什麼事情⋯⋯\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7c80f58f-8026-4840-8afe-38f2ddbbd0ed/1280.jpeg\nhttps://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2baa8d69-4f80-4a35-8179-806ff40ce52d/1280.jpeg","excerpt":"我目前是跟白沙屯媽祖走，我家人沒有非常同意我怎麼做，但我也少去宮裡，大概平均兩個月一次，有媽祖活動才會去幫忙的那種，昨天媽祖盛事剛結束，我帶了求的米回來，我媽又很生氣，叫我不要再去了裝神弄鬼，結果回家","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"37a78696-f6a6-48ec-a19f-688f799a2aed","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-02-03T16:54:14.427Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T16:54:14.427Z","commentCount":26,"likeCount":9,"tags":[],"topics":["親身經歷","真實故事","宗教","靈異板系列文","神明"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"靈異","forumAlias":"marvel","school":"萬能科技大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":9}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7c80f58f-8026-4840-8afe-38f2ddbbd0ed/1280.jpeg"},{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/2baa8d69-4f80-4a35-8179-806ff40ce52d/1280.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"babc1c42-5d0e-4c89-9eb8-3bb76b1b4dc7","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7c80f58f-8026-4840-8afe-38f2ddbbd0ed/640.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7c80f58f-8026-4840-8afe-38f2ddbbd0ed/640.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/7c80f58f-8026-4840-8afe-38f2ddbbd0ed/640.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-02-03T16:54:14.427Z","updatedAt":"2020-02-03T16:54:14.427Z","width":360,"height":640},{"id":"babc1c42-5d0e-4c89-9eb8-3bb76b1b4dc7